  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this RCT is to determine the results of opening-wedge high tibial osteotomy in
      patients with genovarum deformity using iliac crest allograft compared to the results when
      using iliac crest autograft.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
